cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

The paper proposes an algorithm for generating masks for machine learning tasks, specifically for image segmentation. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. The algorithm is also based on machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could be relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with image processing and manipulation, which could also be relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
